{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Yang Istimewa dari Edisi #800 Komik The Amazing Spider-Man","content":"<p>Di dunia komik superhero Amerika, sebuah edisi <em>landmark/milestone</em> selalu berkesan istimewa. Selain sebagai sebuah pembuktian langsung kalau komik tersebut dapat terus laku terjual, terutama di tengah situasi penurunan volume penjualan yang dialami tidak hanya satu namun dua raksasa<em> publisher</em> komik superheroes seperti DC Comics plus <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mirip-dc-comics-rebirth-marvel-comics-meluncurkan-fresh-start/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Marvel Comics</a> sekaligus, komik yang mencapai angka <em>landmark/milestone</em> juga dapat menjadi satu koleksi yang mungkin berharga tinggi di masa depan.</p>\n<p>Itu juga salah satu alasan mengapa saya ngotot membeli<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/merayakan-action-comics-edisi-ke-1000-kenapa-superman-celana-dalamnya-di-depan-ini-jawabannya/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em> Action Comics</em> #1000 dari DC Comics</a> jauh-jauh dari negara asalnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48542\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48542\" data-attachment-id=\"48542\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Instagram&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48542\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48542\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Instagram</p></div></p>\n<p>Rasanya seru banget memiliki komik yang sudah mencapai angka <em>landmark/milestone</em>. Seakan-akan menjadi bagian sebuah sejarah panjang. Dan saat ini komik superhero lain yang akan segera menyentuh angka <em>landmark/milestone</em> seperti <em>Action Comics</em> edisi ke-seribu itu adalah komik superhero dari Marvel Comics: <em>The Amazing Spider-Man.</em></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48543\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48543\" data-attachment-id=\"48543\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Edisi #800. (Sumber: Wikia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48543\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48543\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Edisi #800. (Sumber: Wikia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Spider-Man adalah karakter komik kesayangan fans Marvel. Karakter asli dari Spider-Man adalah Peter Parker, yang mendapatkan kekuatan super karena digigit laba-laba beracun akibat radiasi radioaktif. Karakter komik ciptaan dua legenda Marvel Comics, Stan Lee dan Steve Ditko, ini muncul perdana di komik “Amazing Fantasy #15” tahun 1962 dan menjadi hits serta berubah ke arah komik <em>franchise</em> dimana kemudian karakter serta dunia Spider-Man di-ekspansi; tergantung siapa yang menulis cerita serta siapa yang menggambar <em>art</em>-nya. Tentu bukan hal aneh di dunia komik superheroes Amerika.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48544\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48544\" data-attachment-id=\"48544\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Co-creator Spider-Man, Steve Ditko. (Sumber: ComicBookDaily)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48544\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48544\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Co-creator Spider-Man, Steve Ditko. (Sumber: ComicBookDaily)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat ini, komik Spider-Man juga ada beberapa jenis dengan berbagai tema serta penulis/penggambar. Karakter Spider-Man sendiri lantas tidak hanya Peter Parker. Ada pula nanti Miles Morales.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48545\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48545\" data-attachment-id=\"48545\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spider-Man Miles Morales dan Spider-Man Peter Parker. (Sumber: Marvel Wikia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48545\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48545\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spider-Man Miles Morales dan Spider-Man Peter Parker. (Sumber: Marvel Wikia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Komik Spider-Man yang kini mencapai edisi ke-800, “<em>The Amazing Spider-Man</em>”, ditulis kisahnya oleh Dan Slott. Edisi #801 nanti juga menandai selesainya kiprah Dan Slott di komik The Amazing Spider-Man. Untuk edisi <em>finale</em> ini, Slott mengeluarkan ‘semua senjatanya’ dengan memunculkan musuh-musuh klasik Spider-Man seperti Norman Osborn. Tak cukup dengann Green Goblin itu, Cletus Kasady alias Carnage juga akan muncul. Sebagai <em>symbiote</em>, Carnage akan <em>‘gattai’</em> alias bergabung dengan Osborn dan menjadi Red Goblin yang kuat serta nyaris tanpa kelemahan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48546\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48546\" data-attachment-id=\"48546\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Red Goblin! (Sumber: InsidePulse)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48546\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48546\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Red Goblin! (Sumber: InsidePulse)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di tengah situasi tersebut muncul solusi tak terpikirkan dari Jonah J. Jameson (fans Spider-Man tentu tidak asing dengan nama ini) yang melibatkan <em>symbiote</em> lainnya, <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Venom</a>.</p>\n<p><em>Symbiote</em> hanya dapat diatasi dengan <em>symbiote</em>? Tanpa ada pilihan lain, Peter terpaksa berurusan dengan Venom dan mereka bergabung kembali, seperti yang dulu pernah mereka lakukan sebelum Venom menemukan Eddie Brock sebagai <em>host</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48547\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48547\" data-attachment-id=\"48547\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spidey kembali berkostum symbiote?! (Sumber: Polygon)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48547\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48547\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spidey kembali berkostum symbiote?! (Sumber: Polygon)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di edisi ke-800 komik The Amazing Spider-Man setebal 80 halaman ini akan terdapat banyak hal keren dan mengejutkan fans. Termasuk akan adanya kematian karakter penting. Kejutan-kejutan ini cukup menyenangkan, dan sebaiknya diketahui langsung dengan cara membacanya.</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>*Spoiler alert!*</em></strong></h3>\n<p>Satu kejutan keren di komik Amazing Spider-Man #800 adalah saat Jonah J. Jameson mengetahui kalau Eddie Brock adalah Venom. Hal seru lainnya adalah saat Doc Ock (alias Otto Octavius aka. Doctor Octopus) dan Spider-Man melupakan perselisihan dan bergabung demi menghadapi Red Goblin; seperti yang Peter lakukan saat bergabung dengan Venom.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48548\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48548\" data-attachment-id=\"48548\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yang-istimewa-dari-edisi-800-komik-the-amazing-spider-man/attachment/spide7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"spide7\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CBR&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48548\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/spide7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48548\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CBR</p></div></p>\n<p>Musuh bebuyutan jadi rekan. <em>My enemy’s enemy is my friend</em>. Kematian karakter penting di <em>universe</em>-nya Spider-Man… Komik Amazing Spider-Man edisi ke-seribu menjanjikan hal-hal keren dan seru untuk fans karakter komik ini. Dan Slott serta team di Marvel Comics tidak menahan diri dan memberikan semua yang mereka punya di edisi <em>milestone/landmark</em> Amazing Spider-Man kali ini.</p>\n<p>Kalau kamu seorang fans berat Spider-Man maupun Marvel Comics, kamu seharusnya memiliki edisi <em>milestone/landmark</em> seperti ini sebagai bagian dari koleksi. Sebagai kenang-kenangan pekerjaan terakhir Dan Slott di komik Amazing Spider-Man. Karena bisa dipastikan kalau di edisi #802 nanti, komik <em>franchise</em> ini akan ditangani oleh penulis dan tim baru.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e568e198-d8e8-5204-891c-5731085e15b2"}}}